<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="First2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">First,</orth> adv. 1) before any other: <cit><quote>mine eye loves it and doth f. begin,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 114.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 114, 14</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>which f. begins to crow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 29</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.320" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 320</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.75" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 4.1.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. IV, 1, 38</bibl> etc. etc.<lb />2) before any thing else in order of proceeding: <cit><quote>having f. seized his books,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 2, 97</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 2, 97</bibl> <cit><quote>do the murder f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.232.97" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 232</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.120.97" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 120</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.262" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 262</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.5.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 5, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.362.10" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 362</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.362.10" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 362</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 2, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.116" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 2</bibl> etc. Hence == sooner, rather: <cit><quote>I'll be hanged f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.178" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 178</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the stars will kiss the valleys f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.206" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 206</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll see her damned f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.169" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 169</bibl></cit>.
<lb />3) the first time, at the beginning: <cit><quote>as you were when f. your eye I eyed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 104.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 104, 2</bibl></cit>; cf. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 1, 19</bibl>. <cit><quote>a flower that dies when f. it gins to bud,</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 171" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 171</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>when thou camest f. thou strokedst me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.332" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 332</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.69" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.6.69" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.6.69" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 6</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.6.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 6, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 2, 7</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 5.261.7" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 261</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.6.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 6, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.256" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 256</bibl> etc.
<lb />4) originally: <cit><quote>for a woman wert thou f. created, till Nature, as she wrought thee, fell a doting,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 20.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 20, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I am all the subjects that you have, which f. was mine own king,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.342" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 342</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou camest from Corinth f.?</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 5.362" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 362</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>f. he was a noble servant to them, but he could not carry his honours even,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.7.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 7, 35</bibl></cit>.
<lb />5) in the first place, firstly: <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 1, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 110</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.1.169" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 1, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.255" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.107.4" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 10</bibl> etc.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>